Subject: ixgbe: fix too early devlink_free() in ixgbe_remove()
Patch-mainline: v6.18-rc2
Git-commit: 5feef67b646d8f5064bac288e22204ffba2b9a4a
References: git-fixes CVE-2025-40091 bsc#1252915

Since ixgbe_adapter is embedded in devlink, calling devlink_free()
prematurely in the ixgbe_remove() path can lead to UAF. Move devlink_free()
to the end.

